title: Stowmarket death probe as two bodies found in house on quiet residential street
text:
Stowmarket death probe as two bodies found in house on quiet residential street 
Cops were called to the address in Stowmarket, Suffolk at around 1.45pm yesterday Breaking A MAN and woman were found dead at a house yesterday, sparking a major police probe. 
Cops were called to the address in Stowmarket, Suffolk at around 1.45pm yesterday. BBC Radio Suffolk A man and a woman have been found dead at a property in Stowmarket 
Two bodies were found on arrival. 
The deaths are being treated as unexplained and an investigation is underway. 
Suffolk Police remain at the scene and a cordon is in place. 
The identities of the man and woman have not yet been released.
